{"tid":2251061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國大選] [分析文] 賓州今日截止註冊，至截止前共和黨選民大幅領先","createTime":"2020-10-20T13:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T03:02:07.000Z","uid":52658,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"89b10f4b3cd0fb33c0393043b281304396d0fbc2","tid":2251061,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T13:43:12.000Z","msg":"共和黨 +205,155<br />\n民主黨  -10,266<br />\n<br />\n2016年 川普賓州勝68,000票<br />\n2012年 歐巴馬賓州勝310,000票<br />\n<br />\n川普支持者56%表示會去投票<br />\n拜登支持者35%表示會去投票<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-09-23/469178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-09-23%2F469178&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=19b46a4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-09-23/469178</a><br />\n<br />\n假設2016年至今 藍紅支持者情況無變動<br />\n<br />\n2008 2012及2016年 賓州民主黨得票均約2,900,000<br />\n所以從而推斷 賓州民主黨基本盤約為300萬<br />\n<br />\n2008及2012 共和黨賓州得票約260萬<br />\n2016共和黨得290萬票<br />\n所以共和黨賓州基本盤約280票<br />\nSource:<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/2016_United_States_presidential_election\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2016_United_States_presidential_election&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=b6bd5dbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/2016_United_States_presidential_election</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/2012_United_States_presidential_election\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2012_United_States_presidential_election&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=98ba2fbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/2012_United_States_presidential_election</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/2008_United_States_presidential_election\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2008_United_States_presidential_election&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=490340db\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/2008_United_States_presidential_election</a><br />\n<br />\n結論<br />\n今屆賓州 <br />\n共和黨：280萬+20萬 = 300萬<br />\n民主黨：無變動<br />\n<br />\n但唔好唔記得上面講過<br />\n川普支持者有56%會投票<br />\n所以今屆賓州 川普絕對有機會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dffa75430264761ff19a0ada1bf02e46c59b9ee","tid":2251061,"uid":286897,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T13:46:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d7d53a3daa223b54c6f2a9223972d5d4b59d241","tid":2251061,"uid":66087,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T13:48:10.000Z","msg":"侵侵今次應該會大勝，贏到呀媽都唔認得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b082613a5eaf0cbf76f974321d51f7488836481","tid":2251061,"uid":121146,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"美國啲民調公司都應該執得"},{"pid":"adad3c019765739262df564963b343336b5d8896","tid":2251061,"uid":52658,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5d7d53a3daa223b54c6f2a9223972d5d4b59d241","tid":2251061,"uid":66087,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T13:48:10.000Z","msg":"侵侵今次應該會大勝，贏到呀媽都唔認得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T13:51:39.000Z","msg":"喂<br />\n我無講過佢會大勝 <br />\n唔好屈我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後14日黎鞭鳩我屍<br />\n我係話佢有機會姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b6163ae46dd0d42a417b27b3ae68ad69899415","tid":2251061,"uid":17490,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T13:54:33.000Z","msg":"佛羅里達州咩情況？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgm